*Ovih* dana će biti veoma hladno. (These days it will be very cold.)

*Ovim* se može lako rešiti problem. (This can easily solve the problem.)

*Ovih* je problema bilo preko noći. (These problems were overnight.)

*Ovima* se ne može verovati. (You can't trust these ones.)

*Ovim* se mora postupati pažljivo. (One must proceed carefully with this.)